Description: The official website of the European Union contains a section about agencies and decentralized bodies in the EU. This data is provided as a set of lists- which provide the name of the institutions- as well as links to a detail page about each of them. Most of these pages are available in different languages. If you want to browse the data- please use the links in the "navigation box" on the left side. Furthermore- it is possible to create your own SPARQL queries for obtaining lists of combined information.This dataset (http://agencies.publicdata.eu/) was triplified and published by the research group AKSW (Agile Knowledge Engineering and Semantic Web). For further information about AKSW please visit our website.
